[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     15[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Priority breakdown: 0 critical issues, 2 high issues, 4 medium issues, 3 low issues.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     16[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
